<div class="container py-5">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-5">About Us</h2>

  <!-- Section 1: Our Mission and Vision -->
  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
      <h3>Our Mission</h3>
      <p>
        At Local Service Finder, our mission is to connect homeowners and
        businesses with the best service providers in their area. We strive to
        make finding trusted, reliable, and professional local services easy,
        whether you're looking for plumbing, electrical repairs, or home
        cleaning.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Our Vision</h3>
      <p>
        Our vision is to revolutionize how people find and book services by
        providing a seamless and efficient platform. We aim to ensure quality
        services are accessible to everyone, promoting a hassle-free user
        experience for all service needs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 2: Why Choose Us -->
  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Why Choose Us</h3>
      <p>
        We take pride in offering a curated selection of skilled service
